fields.name: Ivysaur
fields.pokedex_entry: When the bulb on its back grows large, it appears to lose the ability to stand on its hind legs.

fields.name: Venusaur
fields.pokedex_entry: Its plant blooms when it is absorbing solar energy. It stays on the move to seek sunlight.
